            "text": " is a masterpiece, through-and-through. Despite any personal nitpick that can be concocted if I squint my eyes and think pessimistically enough, this game's stellar top-down combat, awe-inspiring presentation and melancholic plot that isn't afraid to have a cheeky laugh will stick with me forever. ",
